Lingua::TR::Numbers
===================

Converts numbers into Turkish text.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

None.

